snippet.title: Mystic Town: THE ABYSS (Intergalacto-1) Official Trailer -THE CHANGE
snippet.description:
After a failed launch day, we've decided to bring major changes to our game. The update is live now with a playable demo—make sure to check it out!

This trailer only showcases Mystic Town: The Abyss, not the entire game content.

Do join our Discord for more updates (for giveaway)
https://discord.gg/Kqx7ghmwtJ

Check out our Steam game page and download now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2990800/Intergalacto1/
